name: Air Canada 787-9 Dreamliner [C-FRSI] Dusk Takeoff from Calgary Airport ᴴᴰ
description:
Seen here, Air Canada's newest Dreamliner (C-FRSI) was delivered to Toronto on February 13th, still in the old livery, 4 days after the reveal. This aircraft is likely the last new aircraft to be painted in AC's former livery, and is seen here taxiing to and departing runway 35R at Calgary International Airport for a dusk departure to Frankfurt. ATC is included, hope you enjoy!

Thanks for watching!
